<head>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="#19202b">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#19202b">
    <meta name="msapplication-navbutton-color" content="#19202b">
</head>

<div class="app-card-container keep-away-nav">
    <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <hr>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "newprofilepic.jpg", width: 500, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
                
                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                        <div class="skill">
                            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div 
                                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-danger"
                                  role="progressbar"
                                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                                  aria-valuemax="100"
                                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                                  ></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>I am a Junior at Cottonwood High School who's dream is to become a great programmer. I am also an avid Marvel and Star Wars fan. I enjoy racing my junior dragster and I have one win, and two runner-ups, under my belt.</p>
                
                <p>I believe I have a responsibility to do good in this world. And I believe I can achieve this through coding.</p>
                
                <p>"With great power comes great responsibility." - Uncle Ben</p>
                
                <p>
                    <button
                      class="btn btn-outline-info"
                      type="button"
                      data-toggle="collapse"
                      data-target="#jobHistory"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controler="jobHistory"
                    >
                        Job History ▼
                    </button>
                    <button
                      class="btn btn-outline-info"
                      type="button"
                      data-toggle="collapse"
                      data-target="#education"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controler="education"
                    >
                        Education ▼
                    </button>
                    <button
                      class="btn btn-outline-info"
                      type="button"
                      data-toggle="collapse"
                      data-target="#awards"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controler="awards"
                    >
                        Awards/Certificates ▼
                    </button>
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Vista Elementary School Sweeper
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Taylorsville High School Sweeper
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Current: V-Chocolates Salesman 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="collapse" id="education">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            GTI Programming 1 & 2
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Code to success 2017
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="collapse" id="awards">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Kiwanis "Hope of America" Award
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Kiwanis "Freedom Leadership" Award
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Utah Education Programming 1 Proficiency Certificates
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Code to success certificate of completion
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>